metadata.name: By that point, no one remembered living in a different way.
metadata.description:
In the process of growth, collapse, and renewal, this fictional being has transformed into a posthuman plastic cyborg. This being is a living relic that has completely turned intelligence around to throw the first stone again.



Artist: Pablo Cotama

Title: By that point, no one remembered living in a different way.
